"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-bears-news-jonathan-owens-simone-biles-husband-special-exemptio-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Being a professional athlete can be complicated, especially managing life outside your career.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 94, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It becomes even trickier when you are in a relationship with another sportsperson, like gymnast Simone Biles andChicago Bearssafety Jonathan Owens.\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 191, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\", \"score\": 0.9999928980971419, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonathan Owens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Late July is a busy time for Biles and Owens, respectively.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unsurprisingly, the former qualified for the Paris 2024Summer Olympicsstarting on the 26th after triumphing at the U.S. trials event this past weekend.\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 349, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996532720307, \"rank\": 3.467280553485945e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By doing so, she made history, becoming the\\u00c2oldest female\\u00c2\\u00a0acrobat to accomplish the remarkable feat.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the latter will be gearing up for the upcoming NFL campaign --\\u00c2veterans begin reporting\\u00c2\\u00a0to Bears training camp on the 23rd of the month.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_NFL_season\", \"score\": 0.7318991243926494, \"rank\": 0.28382952496589847, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_NFL_season\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_NFL_season\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, the possibility of Owens being in attendance to root for his wife at the international multi-sport event seemed murky at best.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, love conquers all, and the Bears appear to understand that.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Per ESPN's Adam Schefter, Chicago will allow Owens to travel to France and cheer on his wife at the Olympics:  Bears are granting Jonathan Owens special permission to leave training camp to support his wife at the Olympics.pic.twitter.com/iRlqeR8Gu6  On Sunday, Biles\\u00c2disclosed\\u00c2\\u00a0to Nancy Armour of USA Today that the Bears have given Owens some excused absences from the offseason workout program.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2067493094201451e-12, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Schefter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Schefter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Schefter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Schefter\"}, {\"begin\": 944, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.9984056858046313, \"rank\": 0.0009570856971745081, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}, {\"begin\": 982, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7000438756688856, \"rank\": 0.2672479778321425, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\", \"score\": 0.9999928980971419, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonathan Owens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Owens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Bears are actually granting him a couple days off from training camp, so he will be there, yes,\\\" Biles told Armour.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For just a short little time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, it will be a quick trip for Owens.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Biles is just happy she can have her husband alongside her.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Anytime we can show up for one another in support, we just get super excited because our schedules do not align that much,\\\" Biles added.\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So whenever it does, it's really important for the both of us to show up in support.\\\"\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Owens spent 2023 with Chicago's divisional rival, the Green Bay Packers, though he signed a two-year, $4.75 million contract with the Bears in March.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.9984056858046313, \"rank\": 0.0009570856971745081, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chicago is now buttering up the veteran defensive back by letting him voyage to the City of Lights to encourage Biles in the flesh.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.9984056858046313, \"rank\": 0.0009570856971745081, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last season, Owens recorded 84 combined tackles, three pass deflections, a sack, a forced fumble and a recovery (which he returned for a touchdown).\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kudos to the Bears for handling the situation with class.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026Minute Media-All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Minute Media or its affiliates and related brands.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someon